                                    <material>Stone</material> <objectType>slab</objectType> comprised of <q>medium-grained, well-sorted, quartz cemented, light grey-brown (10YR 6/1-6/2) sandstone.</q><bibl><ptr target ="#EDW2007"/><citedRange unit="page">251</citedRange></bibl>
